  "24-22": (
    caption: [Plectonemic supercoiling. (a) Elec- tron micrograph of plectonemically supercoiled plasmid DNA and (b) an interpretation of the observed structure. The purple lines show the axis of the supercoil; note the branching of the supercoil. (c) An idealized representation of this structure. c24GenesAndChromosomes.indd Page 993 12/10/12 10:34 AM user-F408 c24GenesAndChromosomes.indd Page 993 12/10/12 10:34 AM user-F408 /Users/user-F408/Desktop /Users/user-F408/Desktop],
