    caption: [Nucleosomes. (a) Regularly spaced nucleosomes consist of core histone proteins bound to DNA. (b) In this electron micrograph, the DNA-wrapped histone octamer structures are clearly visible. 50 nm],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
